parameters.name: masterAbout
parameters.value: The first rule of space travel kids is always check out distress beacons. Nine out of ten times it's a ship full of dead aliens and a bunch of free shit! One out of ten times it's a deadly trap, but... I'm ready to roll those dice! Where did you go to, if I may ask?' said Thorin to Gandalf as they rode along.  To look ahead,' said he.  And what brought you back in the nick of time?' Looking behind,' said he.
